column10: One corner of this  intersection is a K-8 school and a second K-5 school, as well as a Recreation Center, all of which include multiple playgrounds and recreational amenities. This intersection is notoriously dangerous- all the neighbors experience this.

ACPS school bus #116 ran the Stop sign at Taney and Latham. He was driving away from the schools on Taney in the direction toward Van Dorn. There were three other vehicles at the intersection (all arriving/stopping) - the school bus did not even slow down
